Package com.craftfire.commons.ip

Interface Summary
IPRange An interface that represents an IP range.
 

Class Summary
IPAddress A class that represents an IP address (either IPv4 or IPv6).
IPv4Address A class that represents an IPv4 address.
IPv4IntervalRange An IPRange implementation for IPv4 intervals.
IPv4MaskRange An IPRange implementation for IPv4 masks.
IPv6Address A class that represents an IPv6 address.
IPv6IntervalRange An IPRange implementation for IPv6 intervals.
IPv6MaskRange An IPRange implementation for IPv6 masks.
